latestIgtvVideos.title: A Royal Enfield Himalayan turned into a Hard Tail Chopper
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
In the second episode of Engineered to Thrill, we take a look at probably one of the most outrageous and elegant custom jobs based on a Royal Enfield Himalayan. Custom made to be fit for a Navy Officer, the aptly named Anchor is stunning and is as everything that comes out of the TNT Motorcycles garage, Engineered to Thrill.

Find TNT on Instagram - @tnt_motorcycles

TNT Motorcycles, a set up by close friends, Nitin, Naveen and Yogesh came into existence in the year 2013. Based out of Delhi, their work has captivated interest from the likes of Royal Enfield, with the brand doing collaborations with them on multiple occasions. 

Check out our Moto Gear at https://www.tripmachinecompany.com

The Perfect Baileys Coffee Cocktail to liven up your Lazy Sundays
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
This one is a bit special...especially because all of us involved in making this video have their roots in the South Indian state of Kerala. This is where is the base of this drink stems from and its an all time great - The Chukku Kaapi (Ginger Coffee). This was then paired up with another Mallu (lingo for a person from Kerala) favourite, Whiskey, to make what we call at Trip Machine, the Trippy Chukku Kaapi.

This one is an epic combination of two things that are a blessing during winter so it is sure to keep you warm when the chill hits.

Feat @baristaonbike

Over 7000 kilometers from home, we found ourselves at one of the most iconic moto festivals in the world. Trip Machine made its way to Wheels and Waves — Biarritz, France. 

Bikes, boards, stunning build, wild waves, music, good food, stories, and a whole lot of soul. Here’s a glimpse of the ride we’ll never forget.  Away from home, but right where we belonged.

📍NAVIGATOR by @tripmachineco – freedom in a pouch. 📸: thanks @_flash_motion_ 

Riding a naked bike means every detail matters – I need something compact, tough, and ready to roll.
The Navigator is exactly that.
Six super-strong magnets keep it rock solid on the tank, no matter how rough the ride.
It fits all I need inside, and outside it’s all signature TripMachine style: rugged canvas, premium leather, waterproof YKK zippers, and a touch screen window to follow the GPS without missing a turn.

🎒 From tank pouch to belt bag or sling in seconds.
📱 Fits the iPhone 15 Pro Max with ease.
🌧️ Rain? Bring it on – it’s fully waterproof.

The Navigator is the ultimate solution for riding light, staying organized, and keeping your gear safe – both on and off the bike.

🔗 Swipe through the carousel to see it in action.
